Package io.netty.handler.codec.socksx.v5

Encoder, decoder and their related message types for SOCKSv5 protocol.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Socks5AuthRequest
    An socks auth request.
    Socks5AuthRequestDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5AuthRequest.
    Socks5AuthResponse
    An socks auth response.
    Socks5AuthResponseDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5AuthResponse.
    Socks5CmdRequest
    An socks cmd request.
    Socks5CmdRequestDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5CmdRequest.
    Socks5CmdResponse
    A socks cmd response.
    Socks5CmdResponseDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5CmdResponse.
    Socks5InitRequest
    An socks init request.
    Socks5InitRequestDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5InitRequest.
    Socks5InitResponse
    An socks init response.
    Socks5InitResponseDecoder
    Decodes ByteBufs into Socks5InitResponse.
    Socks5MessageEncoder
    Encodes a Socks5Request and Socks5Response into a ByteBuf.
    Socks5Request
    An abstract class that defines a SocksRequest, providing common properties for Socks5InitRequest, Socks5AuthRequest, Socks5CmdRequest and UnknownSocks5Request.
    Socks5Response
    An abstract class that defines a SocksResponse, providing common properties for Socks5InitResponse, Socks5AuthResponse, Socks5CmdResponse and UnknownSocks5Response.
    UnknownSocks5Request
    An unknown socks request.
    UnknownSocks5Response
    An unknown socks response.
